# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REPO 1 — olympic-paints-forms (GitHub Pages static renderer)
#
# This repo has NO server-side environment — it is a static HTML
# file deployed to GitHub Pages with no build step.
#
# Configuration lives directly in index.html as JS constants:
#
#   const SUPABASE_URL  = 'https://your-project-ref.supabase.co';
#   const SUPABASE_ANON = 'eyJhbGci...your-anon-key';
#
# Replace both placeholder strings in index.html after you create
# the Supabase project. The anon key is safe to embed — Supabase
# RLS ensures it can only read active forms and insert submissions.
#
# No .env file is read or needed for this repo.
# This file exists solely as documentation for future maintainers.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Values to embed in index.html (copy from Supabase → Project Settings → API):
# SUPABASE_URL  = https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_ANON = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.your-anon-key
